<section xml:id="section-vectors_matrices_and_linear_systems_or_equations" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Vectors, matrices and linear systems of equations</title>
    
    <introduction>
        <p>
            In this section, we will learn the basic notions underlying linear algebra: vectors, matrices 
            and linear systems and equations. It will turn out, that essentially everything we learn about
            linear algebra will boil down to these basic concepts.
        </p>
    </introduction>
    
    <xi:include href="subsection-linear_algebra-vectors.ptx" />
   
</section>